{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The town of Deadwood is being terrorized by the ghost of a murderous outlaw in Ghost Encounters: Deadwood - The Collector's Edition! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A PARANORMAL POINT-AND-CLICK ADVENTURE FULL OF INTRIGUE </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grave robbers have unleashed a phantom curse and condemned the entire town. One by one the townsfolk are dropping dead and now it's up to you to save them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> EXPLORE THE FORSAKEN TOWN OF DEADWOOD </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After killing 21 men while he was alive, Blackjack is back to kill many more - you'll be at the edge of your seat trying to figure out what is coming next! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> CHALLENGING POINT-AND-CLICK ADVENTURE STYLE GAMEPLAY </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break Blackjack's evil curse and save the day while enjoying the incredible Point-and-Click and Hidden Object Puzzle Adventure gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> UNIQUE PUZZLES AND HIDDEN OBJECT GAMES </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play your way through over 35 different locations while solving 40+ puzzles and mini-games in search of the ghostly villain Blackjack!!!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/353070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727981207","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/353070/page.bg.jpg?t=1727981207","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/353070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727981207","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/353070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727981207","categories":[{"des